&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Systems Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Systems Engineer serves as a technical lead responsible for the architecture, deployment, and optimization of Boingo’s production, Staging, QA, Beta, and Dev systems. This role bridges high-level infrastructure design with hands-on execution, overseeing complex datacenter operations—including racking, stacking, and cabling—while driving the automation of Ubuntu-based virtualized environments. You will act as a primary technical authority, exercising a high degree of personal responsibility for the systems you create to ensure system reliability across global environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloud-Native Architecture:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the design, installation, and scaling of Kubernetes clusters using Ansible and Terraform to meet the needs of demanding engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Drive the management of all environments (Dev to Production), acting as the primary point of contact for system-wide validation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automation:&lt;/strong&gt; Drive scripting and self-service solutions to reduce administrative overhead and &lt;strong&gt;TOIL&lt;/strong&gt;. Build highly resilient, high-performance, and robust systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Direct datacenter physical layer activities (racking/stacking), ensuring hardware is optimized for performance and scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Agile Orchestration:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead Sprint planning within the Atlassian suite; partner with Network, Development, and QA teams to design creative solutions and resolve problems proactively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Governance &amp;amp; Standards:&lt;/strong&gt; Define, document, and follow standards for system design and implementation. Use accepted change control methodologies to justify and implement improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentorship &amp;amp; Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Foster an environment of cross-training, upskilling the team in Kubernetes expertise and mentoring junior engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Continuously monitor and tune systems using metrics collection to drive maximum efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vendor &amp;amp; Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the technical lead for external vendor relations (Ubuntu, Dell, VMware). Participate in on-call rotations to provide expert 24x7 support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
