&lt;li&gt;Ensure that on-site implementation and operations work is in accordance with Venue and Carrier Agreements, Boingo Project Plans, US wireless industry standards, and local, state, national rules and regulations. Successfully manage and direct project completion to meet corporate revenue goals.&lt;/li&gt;
